---
title: Vietnamese-Style Caramelized Pork Bowls with Marinated Veggies and Nuoc Cham
description: Caramelized ground pork is an absolute game-changer in these Vietnamese-style meat and veggie bowls. Lime-pickled carrots and radishes add brightness and acidity to balance the sweet and savoury pork. Tangy and umami-packed nuoc cham completes the dish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-de-porc-caramelise-a-la-vietnamienne-08b880cc.jpg
